!bench

Here are the [benchmark results](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/run-detail/3f425670-eef6-47b1-9813-7ebca2192ef5) for commit 81be7515493417895769f6d8e126ce8533649bab.
There were [significant changes](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/compare/5d123148-9253-40fc-bf75-6d8146d38ac3/to/3f425670-eef6-47b1-9813-7ebca2192ef5) against commit ede775853cc9f271a9fcf1475dec887f82544e30:
```diff
  Benchmark                                                   Metric         Change
  =================================================================================
+ ~Mathlib.Analysis.Complex.Basic                             instructions   -15.7%
- ~Mathlib.Analysis.SpecificLimits.Basic                      instructions    66.7%
- ~Mathlib.Dynamics.Circle.RotationNumber.TranslationNumber   instructions    32.8%
- ~Mathlib.Topology.Algebra.UniformGroup                      instructions    45.5%
- ~Mathlib.Topology.UniformSpace.Cauchy                       instructions   155.4%
```
!bench

Here are the [benchmark results](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/run-detail/54a2971b-585c-4b8e-90af-e16cc7fd8077) for commit ba84d876cdffe0fd9e2d8dc5063c55354cdf7d80.
There were [significant changes](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/compare/1ceb60c8-ad7f-472c-a823-fe7015c186eb/to/54a2971b-585c-4b8e-90af-e16cc7fd8077) against commit a6bc4c5ee86f2ccb63f6d63406cd3db02d3de29a:
```diff
  Benchmark                                                   Metric         Change
  =================================================================================
+ ~Mathlib.Analysis.Complex.Basic                             instructions   -16.2%
+ ~Mathlib.Dynamics.Circle.RotationNumber.TranslationNumber   instructions   -35.1%
```
Note that improvements in the 2 files come from adding extra hints, not from making `sInf` irreducible.

Pull request successfully merged into master.

  * [Lint style](https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/actions/runs/11415315729/job/31765232794)

Thanks :tada:

bors merge
